    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Continual Flame</strong> (Level 2 Evocation)</p><p>A flame, equivalent in brightness to a torch, springs forth from an object that you touch. The effect looks like a regular flame, but it creates no heat and doesn't use oxygen. A continual flame can be covered or hidden but not smothered or quenched.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (Ruby dust worth 50 gp, which the spell consumes.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> Until dispelled</p><p><em>Classes: Cleric, Wizard</em></p>",
